title: Viharsarok 2014 Hungarian 1280x720p AAC Mkv Makalakato
description:
Hugarian gay movie with english subs.

Trailer:


A powerful story of desire and death, of faith and oppression, of trust and betrayal, and of individual choices that go against the prejudice of society. The director skillfully makes use of an evocative rural landscape as if it was a central character. Underneath a surface of peaceful tranquility, the languid countryside constantly conceals an ominous, threatening menace that could strike the protagonists as a sudden lightning
